<br>
If you are just interested in the Globe, I'd suggest basing out of the entry hall pretty far down (otherwise you will agro random stonegrabbers through the walls... yay). Should be able to pull just the first 2 entry way mobs if you are careful (watch the roamers). They have roughly 3k hp and hit up to around 80. Also have an annoying tendency to resist roots a lot.<br>
<br>
Gives good faction with all factions in Seru, bad faction with Thought Leeches and Recuso. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4380>Qaman</a><BR>
